okay um it starts off with the roadrunner and coyote story

to eat him

with a boxing glove attached to a spring

the roadrunner comes by

to suspend an anvil from two cliffs on a tightrope ?
and the roadrunner walks to the middle of the the tightrope
with the anvil and

ing towards him and leaves
and then uh he’s like he lets go of the anvil
and he’s thrown up into the air

and he he I guess he has a headache or something
and then uh the third one is when
they’re both in the mines

they’re like caves

the roadrunner keeps uh taunting him
